ian-mission-south-china-sea-2024-05-15/</link><description>菲律宾已派出三艘海岸警卫队船只，以确保驶往南海浅滩的民用船队的安全。马尼拉和北京在该海域因主权争议而陷入激烈对峙。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 07:23:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-ensure-safety-civilian-mission-south-china-sea-2024-05-15/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国的军事入侵正在逼近台湾</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-military-incursions-inch-closer-taiwan-sources-say-2024-05-15/</link><description>据台湾政府报告称，最近几周，中国军队的航行和飞行距离比以往更接近台湾，并在台湾下任总统周一就职之前对外国船只进行了模拟攻击。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 06:41:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-military-incursions-inch-closer-taiwan-sources-say-2024-05-15/</guid></item><item><title>Burberry在华销量大幅下滑，利润暴跌34%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/burberrys-profit-slumps-34-luxury-demand-slows-2024-05-15/</link><description>英国奢侈品牌巴宝莉 (Burberry) 周三报告称，由于其最大市场中国的销售额在最后一个季度大幅下滑，其年度营业利润下降了 34%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 06:15:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/burberrys-profit-slumps-34-luxury-demand-slows-2024-05-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国部分地区公用事业价格上涨给家庭带来又一次打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/utility-price-hikes-parts-china-hand-another-blow-households-2024-05-15/</link><description>中国十多个城市的公用事业价格上涨可能会暂时将全国通胀从超低水平提升，但最终可能会成为全球第一大经济体的通货紧缩力量。分析师表示，2.0经济进一步削弱了家庭的消费能力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 04:27:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/utility-price-hikes-parts-china-hand-another-blow-households-2024-05-15/</guid></item><item><title>彭博新闻社称，中国考虑地方政府购买未售出的房屋</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-considers-government-purchases-unsold-homes-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-05-15/</link><description>彭博新闻社周三称，在执政的共产党领导人召开会议呼吁努力清理不断增加的住房库存后，中国正在考虑一项让全国地方政府购买数百万套未售出房屋的计划。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 03:34:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-considers-government-purchases-unsold-homes-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-05-15/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称世卫组织应让其参加所有会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-who-should-let-it-attend-all-its-meetings-2024-05-15/</link><description>台湾外交部长吴钊燮周三呼吁世界卫生组织，如果台湾认真对待“人人享有健康”的目标，在台北希望参加的一次重要峰会之前，允许台湾参加所有会议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 02:30:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-who-should-let-it-attend-all-its-meetings-2024-05-15/</guid></item><item><title>成功推出SU7后，小米成为中国第八大电动汽车新贵</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-becomes-8th-largest-ev-upstart-china-after-successful-su7-launch-2024-05-15/</link><description>根据行业数据，中国智能手机制造商小米已成为中国第八大电动汽车新贵，其首款车型 SU7 轿车 4 月份销量超过 7,000 辆。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 02:21:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-becomes-8th-largest-ev-upstart-china-after-successful-su7-launch-2024-05-15/</guid></item><item><title>通胀前股市创历史新高；模因狂热升温</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-15/</link><description>周三，全球股市上涨，美元下跌，此前美国批发通胀的热门数据为消费者价格报告之前的交易奠定了紧张的基调，消费者价格报告可能对美联储降息具有决定性作用。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 02:08:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行维持主要政策利率不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-leaves-key-policy-rate-unchanged-matching-forecast-2024-05-15/</link><description>周三，中国央行在展期到期中期借贷便利（MLF）贷款时维持关键政策利率不变，符合市场预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 01:39:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-leaves-key-policy-rate-unchanged-matching-forecast-2024-05-15/</guid></item><item><title>华为中国旗舰店激增，预示着与苹果的摊牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-flagship-store-surge-china-signals-showdown-with-apple-2024-05-15/</link><description>华为正在调整其零售战略，并积极在中国开设旗舰店，其中一些旗舰店距离苹果商店仅一箭之遥，以期夺回全球最大智能手机市场的高端电子产品宝座。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 01:03:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-flagship-store-surge-china-signals-showdown-with-apple-2024-05-15/</guid></item><item><title>普京支持中国的乌克兰和平计划，称北京理解冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-backs-chinas-ukraine-peace-plan-says-beijing-understands-conflict-2024-05-15/</link><description>俄罗斯总统在接受采访时表示，他仍然愿意通过对话和谈判来解决这场持续两年多的冲突。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 00:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-backs-chinas-ukraine-peace-plan-says-beijing-understands-conflict-2024-05-15/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯普京无视西方，将在北京会见习近平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/defying-west-russias-putin-due-meet-xi-jinping-beijing-2024-05-14/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京(Vladimir Putin)周四的北京之行可能不会达成硬协议，但将标志着他新总统任期的开始，他最强大的政治伙伴、中国国家主席习近平将表示支持。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 22:03:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/defying-west-russias-putin-due-meet-xi-jinping-beijing-2024-05-14/</guid></item></channel></rss>